{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/socketclient\/onnotifytimeout(flags:handler:)"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketClient","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketClient\/SocketClientProtocol-Implementations"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"onNotifyTimeout","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO15SocketClientRefV","text":"SocketClientRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketClientRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"flags","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"handler","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Run the given callback whenever the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notifyTimeout"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"text":" call, like this:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"syntax":"C"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::timeout"},{"text":" signal","type":"text"}]}]}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"onNotifyTimeout(flags:handler:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyTimeout"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"text":"SocketClientRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO15SocketClientRefV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"extendedModule":"GIO","externalID":"s:3GIO20SocketClientProtocolPAAE15onNotifyTimeout5flags7handlerSi10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0bC3RefV_AG09ParamSpecN0VtctF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO12SocketClientC","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketClient\/onNotifyTimeout(flags:handler:)"},"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emit